  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6776 sitting above the GEX flip at 6746 in a PIN regime, dealers are long gamma and will sell into strength as we approach the massive +5.6B wall at 6800. The recent GEX surge event combined with heavy positive gamma concentration between 6750-6900 creates a strong mean-reverting environment where dealers will aggressively fade moves in either direction. Key resistance comes at 6800 where dealer selling pressure peaks, while support builds at 6750 (+2.6B) with the flip point at 6746 acting as the critical pivot for regime change.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect price to get pinned between 6750-6800 with limited breakout potential.",
